OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing somewhat during the evening but
OL,7,Flingering for much of around some
OL,8,Fcoastal counties. Remaining largely
OL,9,Fcloudy and generally mild, though
OL,10,Fchillier under any prolonged clear
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy start for many on
OL,14,Fbank holiday Monday, with a few bright
OL,15,For sunny spells emerging. Further
OL,16,Fshowers are likely to bubble up during
OL,17,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
